CH3 NOTES

Input Characters From The Keyboard:
	System.in.read() returns an integer value and must be cast to a char if assigned to char variable.

If Statement:
	if(condition) statement;
	else statement;

	if(condition){
		statement sequence
	}else{
		statement sequence
	}

Switch Statement:
	switch(expression){
		case constant1:
			statement sequence
			break;
		case constant2:
			statement sequence
			break;
		.
		.
		.
		case constantN:
			statement sequence
			break;
		default:
			statement sequence
	}
